## 🔒 Security Protocol
* **Firebase App Check:** Prevents unauthorized API access from non-app sources.
* **Firestore Rules:** Attribute-Based Access Control (ABAC) ensuring users only see their own data.
* **Crashlytics:** Real-time monitoring of app stability across the Birnin Kebbi device ecosystem.
